TzHaar-Ket-Yil is the only banker in the inner area of Mor Ul Rek. There is a poll booth, deposit box, and bank chest located in the bank area.

The bank is found relatively close to the Inferno, allowing player to quickly resupply for an attempt at completing the minigame.
